  "texts": [
    "Figure 5: Bloom's Level Relative ProportionWe anticipate that these and other insights can provide useful information as the course progresses for intervention by the teaching team.",
    "The chatbot architecture that we developed can serve as the basis for future developments.",
    "Incorporating a memory, so that the chatbot can respond conversationally, is a key priority.",
    "In addition, extending the retrieval functionality to also indicate to the student where they can look in the course documents for further information can be beneficial in helping them to search and understand the documentation for themselves.The analytics that can be generated from logging data may lead to interesting insights into how courses run, and how students attempt to get their questions answered.",
    "More research is needed into the best form these analytics can take in order to maximize the effectiveness of these interventions.Self-hosting a chatbot can break down barriers to access LLM technology, can increase the chances that chatbot interactions are course-aligned, and can provide valuable insights into student learning."
